<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN210-intro">
      <p type="edition">tiṇaiyum tuṟaiyum avai. cēramāṉa kuṭakkōccēralirumpoṟai piricaṉīṭṭittāṉaip peruṅkuṉṟūrkiḻār pāṭiyatu.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en" type="translation">  
      </p>
  </div>
    <div xml:id="PN210">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>maṉpatai kākkuniṉ puraimai nōkkā</l>
<l>taṉpukaṇ māṟiya vaṟaṉil kāṭciyoṭu</l>
<l>numma ṉōrumaṟ ṟiṉaiya rāyi</l>
<l>ṉemma ṉōrivaṭ piṟavalar mātō</l>
<l>ceyirtīr koḷkai yemveṅ kātali</l>
<l>yuyirciṟi tuṭaiya ḷāyi ṉemvayi</l>
<l>ṉuḷḷā tiruttalō varitē yataṉā</l>
<l>laṟaṉil kūṟṟan tiṟaṉiṉṟu tuṇiyap</l>
<l>piṟaṉā yiṉaṉko liṟīiyareṉ ṉuyireṉa</l>
<l>nuvalvuṟu ciṟumaiyaḷ palapulan tuṟaiyu</l>
<l>miṭukkaṇ maṉaiyō ṭīriya vinnilai</l>
<l>viṭuttaṉaṉ vāḻiyar kuruci lutukkā</l>
<l>ṇavala neñcamoṭu celvaṉiṟ kaṟuttō</l>
<l>raruṅkaṭi muṉaiyaraṇ pōlap</l>
<l>peruṅkai yaṟṟaveṉ pulampumun tuṟuttē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l corresp="1">Not looking at your greatness that guards humanity, </l>
<l corresp="2">with virtueless sight that has changed from love, </l>
<l corresp="3">if the likes of you are like this </l>
<l corresp="4">should the likes of us be born here? </l>
<l corresp="5">The beloved who is keen on us, with blemishless principles, </l>
<l>if she possesses a life that is small, without thinking</l>
<l>about us, as for living [on], that is difficult. Therefore (6f.)</l>
<l corresp="8">“When the power of virtueless Death is determined today, </l>
<l corresp="9">has he become another (~ is he dead)? May my life break”, </l>
<l corresp="10">with a despondency that experienced talking [of that kind] she remains much vexed. </l>
<l corresp="11">So that the affliction of her in the house ends, from this position </l>
<l corresp="12">I take leave. Live [long]. lord – see here: </l>
<l corresp="13a-c">I go with a heavy heart, </l>
<l corresp="15">placing before me my loneliness that is greatly prostrate, </l>
<l corresp="13d-14">like a fortress on the heavily guarded frontier of those who angered you. </l>
</lg>
    </div>
